headline: Canadian Solar Q3 Earnings Surpass Estimates, Revenues Fall Y/Y
summary: CSIQ reported third-quarter revenues of $1.51 billion, which lagged the Zacks Consensus Estimate by 10.7%. The top line also declined 18.3% from the year-ago quarter's level.
